# Context for apps/web/Dockerfile (repo root — pnpm workspace files).
# Host artifacts must never leak into the image: node_modules contains
# host-native binaries, and the image installs its own from the lockfile.
.git
**/node_modules
**/.turbo
**/dist
**/coverage
apps/api/.venv
apps/api/**/__pycache__
e2e/playwright-report
e2e/test-results
docs
episodes
